<dt>Commentary:</dt>
<dd><a href="https://www.rand.org/blog/2021/08/afghanistan-withdrawal-says-little-about-us-commitments.html">Afghanistan Withdrawal Says Little About U.S. Commitments Elsewhere</a></dd>
