<h1 id="RANDTitleHeadingId">What Do Former Extremists and Their Families Say About Radicalization and Deradicalization in America?</h1>
<p class="authors">by <a href="/about/people/b/brown_ryan_andrew.html">Ryan Andrew Brown</a>, <a href="/about/people/h/helmus_todd_c.html">Todd C. Helmus</a>, <a href="/about/people/r/ramchand_rajeev.html">Rajeev Ramchand</a>, <a href="/about/people/p/palimaru_alina_i.html">Alina I. Palimaru</a>, <a href="/about/people/w/weilant_sarah.html">Sarah Weilant</a>, <a href="/about/people/r/rhoades_ashley_l.html">Ashley L. Rhoades</a>, <a href="/about/people/h/hiatt_liisa.html">Liisa Hiatt</a></p>
<ul class="related-topics"><li class="heading">Related Topics: </li><li><a href="/topics/counterterrorism.html">Counterterrorism</a>, </li><li><a href="/topics/domestic-terrorism.html">Domestic Terrorism</a>, </li><li><a href="/topics/the-islamic-state-terrorist-organization.html">The Islamic State (Terrorist Organization)</a>, </li><li><a href="/topics/united-states.html">United States</a>, </li><li><a href="/topics/violent-extremism.html">Violent Extremism</a></li></ul>
<ul class="icon-list"><li class="hide"><button class="citation">Citation</button></li><li><button class="embed hide" data-path="/pubs/research_briefs/RBA1071-1.readonline.html">Embed</button></li><li><a href="#related" class="product-jump">View related products</a></li></ul>
<div class="social-media-buttons">
<ul><li><a class="facebook social-button" data-hover="Share on Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rand.org%2Fpubs%2Fresearch_briefs%2FRBA1071-1.html"><span class="access">Share on Facebook</span></a></li><li><a class="twitter social-button" data-hover="Share on Twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rand.org%2Fpubs%2Fresearch_briefs%2FRBA1071-1.html&amp;text=What+Do+Former+Extremists+and+Their+Families+Say+About+Radicalization+and+Deradicalization+in+America%3F&amp;via=RANDCorporation"><span class="access">Share on Twitter</span></a></li><li><a class="linkedin social-button" data-hover="Share on LinkedIn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rand.org%2Fpubs%2Fresearch_briefs%2FRBA1071-1.html&title=What+Do+Former+Extremists+and+Their+Families+Say+About+Radicalization+and+Deradicalization+in+America%3F"><span class="access">Share on LinkedIn</span></a></li></ul>
